* [[Ernst Haeckel]]<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=pFJvtfRaM48C ''Wonders of Life''] by Ernst Haeckel.</ref><ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=RdsdAAAAMAAJ The Evolution of Man: A Popular Scientific Study, Volume 2] by Ernst Heinrich Philipp August Haeckel.</ref>
* [[Jonathan Schaffer]]
* [[Georgi Plekhanov]]
* [[Friedrich Engels]]
